---
const { last = false } = Astro.props;
---
<section class:list={["block", { "curtain-edge": last }]} id="why">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Why Eli's</span>
      <h2 class="display">More than a haircut.</h2>
      <p>We pair real barbering experience with genuine care and a room you actually want to sit in. Here's what sets the chair apart.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="vcards">
      <article class="vcard reveal">
        <img class="ico" src="/media/Icon-3.png" alt="" />
        <h3>Experienced Barbering</h3>
        <p>Owner Eli Chanimov has spent years mastering the craft, shaping every cut to the person in the chair.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="vcard reveal d1">
        <img class="ico" src="/media/Icon-2.png" alt="" />
        <h3>Quality Cuts, Simple Pricing</h3>
        <p>Honest, flat pricing and consistent quality — no upsells, no surprises, just a great cut.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="vcard reveal d2">
        <img class="ico" src="/media/Icon-4.png" alt="" />
        <h3>Relaxed, Friendly Room</h3>
        <p>A comfortable, welcoming space where everyone gets looked after. Step in, sit back, relax.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
    <div class="why-cta reveal">
      <a class="btn btn--amber" href="tel:+14162242877">Call to book <span class="arw">→</span></a>
      <a class="btn" href="#about">About us <span class="arw">→</span></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
